    RapaGUI was written by Andreas Falkenhahn. The design was inspired by my MUI
    Royale plugin which only runs on AmigaOS and compatibles and was first
    published at the end of 2012. First experiments with a wxWidgets-based GUI
    toolkit for Hollywood were already started in 2013. Initially I just planned
    to create a wrapper plugin that allows Hollywood scripts to use wxWidgets
