        the widget's boundaries. For example, mouse button events won't trigger
        if the mouse button is released when the cursor is outside the widget's
        boundaries. You can change this behaviour by setting Area.MouseCapture
        to TRUE.

        Note that this attribute is currently only implemented for classes Image
