   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        You have to call this method repeatedly in order to animate the widget.
        A good idea is to install a Hollywood interval timer using
        "SetInterval()" and then call this method from the timer about 10 times
        per second or so.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
        id        id of the busybar object

@ENDNODE

