    Linux this class requires WebKitGTK+ to be installed. Since this is not
    available on every system, there is also a separate RapaGUI version without
    this class and thus without a WebKitGTK+ dependency. On AmigaOS and
    compatibles this class requires the HTMLview.mcc extension.

