   @{b}NAME@{ub}
        Label.Text -- set/get label text

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Set or get the label text. If the text contains an underscore, the
        character following the underscore will automatically be highlighted as
        the accelerator key. You can disable this behaviour by setting the
        @{"Area.NoAutoKey" LINK AreaNoAutoKey} attribute.

   @{b}TYPE@{ub}
        String

