@NODE ListviewMove "RapaGUI Guide"

   @{b}NAME@{ub}
        Listview.Move -- move entry to new position

   @{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
        moai.DoMethod(id, "Move", from, to)

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Move the specified entry to a new position. Positions have to be passed
        as absolute values starting from 0 to @{"Listview.Entries" LINK ListviewEntries} -1 or pass one of
        the following special values:

        Top       Use first entry.

        Active    Use active entry.

        Bottom    Use last entry.

        Next      Use next entry. This is only valid for the second parameter.

        Previous  Use previous entry. This is only valid for the second
                  parameter.

        This method can only be used with non-sortable listviews because the
        item order in sortable listviews is fixed and determined solely by the
