@NODE ListviewQuiet "RapaGUI Guide"

   @{b}NAME@{ub}
        Listview.Quiet -- disable listview refresh

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Adding or removing many entries at once is usually quite expensive
        because the widget is refreshed after every add and remove operation.
        Setting Listview.Quiet to TRUE will temporarily turn off listview
        refresh until you set the attribute to FALSE again. This can speed up
        insertion and remove operations significantly in case lots of entries
        are affected.

   @{b}TYPE@{ub}
        Boolean

   @{b}APPLICABILITY@{ub}
        @{"S" LINK Applicability}

@ENDNODE

@NODE ListviewRemove "RapaGUI Guide"

