        Listview.Remove -- remove entry from listview

   @{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
        moai.DoMethod(id, "Remove", pos)

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Remove an entry from a listview. The position can be specified as an
        absolute index value or as one of the following special values:

        First     Remove first entry.

        Active    Remove active entry.

        Last      Remove last entry.

