    You can set the title of the popup dialog using the @{"Popfile.Title" LINK PopfileTitle} attribute
    on the Popfile object and you can get the user's selection by getting the
    @{"Popfile.File" LINK PopfileFile} attribute.

    @{"Popfile.File                      " LINK PopfileFile} Set/get current popfile path
    @{"Popfile.Pattern                   " LINK PopfilePattern} Set filter pattern for file requester
    @{"Popfile.SaveMode                  " LINK PopfileSaveMode} Enable save mode
    @{"Popfile.Title                     " LINK PopfileTitle} Set requester title
@ENDNODE

@NODE PopfileFile "RapaGUI Guide"

   @{b}NAME@{ub}
        Popfile.File -- set/get current popfile path

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Get and set the current path of this popfile object.

        You can also set up a notification on this attribute to be notified
